title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 §§ 62-1.2 - Additional features

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 §§ 62-1.2 - Additional features

State Regulations

All renewal certificates issued in the State of New York shall conform with the foregoing provisions and may contain such additional features as may be approved upon filing with the Superintendent of Insurance. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11
§§
62-1.2

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
